<plot>Aurora is a wedding photographer. Everyday, she shoots pictures of other people's love. When she discovers a gruesome, but strangely compelling and beautiful photograph she tracks down Lukas - the man who took it - a world-weary former war photojournalist. Their relationship careens wildly into very dangerous and provocative territory where they discover their mutual hunger for real life and real pain and where Aurora ultimately discovers her own voice, her own unique passion.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?495427</url></doc>
